==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reasonless
<hw>Rea"son*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Destitute of
reason; <as>as, a <ex>reasonless</ex> man or mind</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Void of reason; not warranted or supported by
reason; unreasonable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This proffer is absurd and <qex>reasonless</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>reassail</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>re-assail</ent>⟦br⟧
